description: This family-run truck has been winning over the bellies of Oklahoma with their insanely delicious chicken dishes. You just must come out and dig right into their cluckin’ cuisine, like the Honey Grilled Chicken on a Stick, Lemon Peppered Chicken Wings, Loaded Baked Potatoes, and so much more. Whether you wish to feed your guests at your next event, or are just lookin’ for your next poultry fix, C-n-D’s Chicken on a Stick is the perfect choice for you, with their delightful variety chicken dinners, all of winner-winner caliber.
name: C-n-D's Chicken on a Stick
